"""
Crypto-focused rubric labelling utility.

This module applies a curated set of sentiment rules (rubrics) to headline/content
pairs and writes user-facing sentiments (super positive ... super negative).

The implementation in this file is intentionally modular, typed, and well-logged so
that new crypto patterns can be added without touching the entire pipeline.
"""

